Plot the Animation

anim <- ggplot(data = iris) +
  geom_point(mapping = aes(x = Sepal.Length, y = Sepal.Width, shape = Species, color = Species)) +
  transition_states(Species,
                    transition_length = 2,
                    state_length = 1)

anim + 
  enter_fade() + 
  exit_shrink()
